      "title": "起来 的特殊用法 — Special Use of 起来",
      "explanation": "Beyond literal 'rise up', 起来 after a verb can mean 'start to' (action begins): 唱起来 = start singing. 笑起来 = start laughing. 看起来 (standalone) = seem/look like. 听起来 = sound like. These extended uses are very common in everyday speech.",
